-- Daimler Trucks Unit Sticks to 2013 Margin Target of 8%
-- B y   D o r o t h e e   T s c h a m p a
-- 2012-06-22T13:48:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-22/daimler-trucks-unit-sticks-to-2013-margin-target-of-8-correct-.html
(Corrects percentage figure in headline.)  Daimler AG’s truckmaking division is
sticking to a target of earnings before interest and taxes in
2013 at 8 percent of sales as it expects to meet goals for this
year, said  Andreas Renschler , the head of the unit.  Brazil’s commercial vehicle market is likely to improve in
the second half of this year, Renschler said in an interview at
an industry conference in Frankfurt.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dorothee Tschampa in Frankfurt at 
